info.name: Japanese Dragon - Roblox
info.description: This is the fixed version of the original, it works. All credits go to this wallpaper site, >Mania<, it lists this image as non-commercial so don't try and profit off this. It is kanji so it's written in Traditional Chinese but is done like this as a Japanese custom. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
info.additionalInfo: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Won't work for tablets/iPads or phones. The style not appearing/downloading bug is an issue with the extension, not style. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. French Translated Help Section - Section d'aide traduite en français - cliquez ici. Russian/Cyrillic Translated Help Section - Русский/кириллица переведенный раздел помощи - кликните сюда. Spanish Translated Help Section - Sección de ayuda traducida al español - haga clic aquí. The original theme was this Japanese Dragon. It's a link. 27 August 2022 - Released 5 November 2022 - Made the navigation and header bars slightly darker in colo(u)r due to a request. 17 April 2023 - Revamped style with new base code.
